#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-03-16-quarkus-2-7-5-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Today, we released 2.7.5.Final which, as usual, only contains bugfixes and documentation improvements."
msgstr "今天，我们发布了2.7.5.Final，像往常一样，它只包含错误修复和文档改进。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-03-16-quarkus-2-7-5-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is a safe upgrade for anyone already using 2.7."
msgstr "对于已经使用2.7的人来说，这是一次安全的升级。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-03-16-quarkus-2-7-5-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are not using 2.7 already, please refer to the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-2.7[2.7 migration guide]."
msgstr "如果你还没有使用2.7，请参考 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-2.7[2.7迁移指南] 。"

